                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>A conference of Military Representatives of the United States, the United
                    Kingdom, France, New Zealand, and Australia met in Washington from October 6 to
                    October 17, 1952, to consider the defense of Southeast Asia in the event of
                    aggression by forces of the People’s Republic of China. For the conclusions of
                    the conference report, October 17, and related documentation, see <ref
                        target="frus1952-54v12p1">volume <hi rend="smallcaps">xii</hi>
                    </ref>.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
